OL,5, A Lanarkshire mum says she has been    
OL,6, failed by the justice system after the 
OL,7, driver who killed her son avoided jail 
OL,8, because of his age.                    
OL,10,FAmanda McIlquham's son Steven died on  
OL,11,FNew Year's Day 2020.                   
OL,13,FThe 15-year-old was walking to his     
OL,14,Fgrandparents' house in Wishaw when he  
OL,15,Fwas hit by a Volkswagen Golf.          
OL,17,FHe was crossing Alexander Street, at   
OL,18,Fits junction with Marshall Street when 
OL,19,F22-year-old Brian Buchanan struck him, 
OL,20,Fdoing 45mph in a 30mph zone.           
